{"tid":1266343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持警察抗暴有功，支持何君堯仗義執言","createTime":"2019-06-29T13:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T16:32:50.000Z","uid":226156,"like":13,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"94a8f506688b85ee6a4075a6af9986600fe41ae4","tid":1266343,"uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"面對暴徒，警察努力守住各個重要行政機構，現在變成過街老鼠，整天承受黃屍言語和行動的欺凌。<br />\n如果在外國，班後生仔早就死了！成班廢青打得少，政府高官卻還強調警員克制，變相容忍黃屍搞事，我真係好憤怒。看見香港這樣，我很難過。幸見何律師仗義執言，教人鬆了一口氣。明天一起出來，支持警隊！<br />\n希望何律師可以邀請各位有份開鎗抗暴，棍打黃屍嘅警察上台除下制服面罩接受大家的掌聲，如能夠提供警員號碼更好，方便我們為你送上感謝信支持你們。"},{"pid":"f98288333d19b222dbcabf94969816006c68329a","tid":1266343,"uid":215794,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"偏頗<br />\n仇恨言論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">負評 不回覆 上一頁</span></span>"},{"pid":"a58a94e5d7de2fe69682d2a8f006e182b9581423","tid":1266343,"uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:57:14.000Z","msg":"撐"},{"pid":"f21a5a7bf8b1dc6a790bb6bab3214cb90a31ca03","tid":1266343,"uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"281c1ffebf6d6f55d979b60d54c2cb81a07a1cb6","tid":1266343,"uid":226156,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"你地唔想見下抗暴有功嘅警察咩？"},{"pid":"1689000a915b780d7d6665995cc66f070be2b1ac","tid":1266343,"uid":264067,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:23:50.000Z","msg":"請睇前文後理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7594c65108195d06d6c0163a08b354a3693847","tid":1266343,"uid":1330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:25:05.000Z","msg":"好多睇完標題就負皮"},{"pid":"9e02993ba2e39248491f9b47ae8ff8a25f91ad68","tid":1266343,"uid":153,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src